<script type="application/ld+json">[{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"Organization","name":"APKPure","url":"https://apkpure.net","logo":"https://static.cdnpure.com/www/static/imgs/logo_new.png","sameAs":["https://www.facebook.com/APKPureOfficial","https://twitter.com/apkpure","https://vk.com/apkpurevk","https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbCOKdnt1yYk4S3I4a034XQ"],"contactPoint":{"@type":"ContactPoint","email":"support@apkpure.net"}},{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"WebSite","name":"APKPure","url":"https://apkpure.net","potentialAction":{"@type":"SearchAction","target":"https://apkpure.net/search?q={search_term_string}","query-input":"required name=search_term_string"}},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"BreadcrumbList","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"name":"Home","item":"https://apkpure.net/"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"name":"Games","item":"https://apkpure.net/game"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"name":"Adventure","item":"https://apkpure.net/game_adventure"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":4,"name":"Summertime Saga","item":"https://apkpure.net/summertime-saga-android-app/com.kompasproductions.summertimesaga"},{"@type":"ListItem","position":5,"name":"Download"}]},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Why can't I install Summertime Saga?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The installation of Summertime Saga may fail because of the lack of device storage, poor network connection, or the compatibility of your Android device. Therefore, please check the minimum requirements first to make sure Summertime Saga is compatible with your phone."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How to download Summertime Saga old versions?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"APKPure provides the latest version and all the older versions of Summertime Saga. You can download any version you want from here: All Versions of Summertime Saga"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What's the file size of Summertime Saga?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Summertime Saga takes up around 874.0 MB of storage. It's recommended to download APKPure App to install Summertime Saga successfully on your mobile device with faster speed."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What language does Summertime Saga support?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Summertime Saga supports isiZulu,中文,Việt Nam, and more languages. Go to More Info to know all the languages Summertime Saga supports. "}}]},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"MobileApplication","name":"Summertime Saga","description":"Developed by DarkCookie and funded by Patreon, this free project grows with regular updates and a lively community. The appeal lies in its large cast and open-ended routes that make each day feel different. You can download Summertime Saga APK for easy access. Below are the core highlights users notice early on.Meet 65+ characters with branching routes and relationship arcs.Explore 30+ locations via map to trigger events and secrets.Play 20+ mini-games tied to jobs, school, and activities.Regular updates, public roadmap, and active wiki/Discord support.Town Exploration and Branching StoriesExploration sits at the center of play, with a map that opens 30+ locations and the freedom to visit them at different times of day. Each spot holds events, characters, and story threads that unlock as you progress. Choices shape dialogue, timing, and where arcs go next, so it often makes sense to revisit places and try alternatives.The Summertime Saga app lets you move through school, home, the gym, and other familiar stops while juggling classes, part-time work, and relationships. A typical session might start with a quick errand that leads to a new scene, then a mini-game, and later an unexpected meet-up. Storylines are ongoing, so content expands over time instead of ending abruptly.Characters and Relationship ProgressWith 65+ characters, the game leans into personalities and recurring interactions. Conversations, favors, and timing build trust and open routes, while certain scenes depend on previous choices and progress. The Cookie Jar serves as a viewer to track unlocked characters and scenes, making it easier to see what you’ve discovered and where gaps remain.In-game, the mobile phone icon brings up a phone UI with useful toggles. Some users visit a hidden Wi‑Fi page that accepts a code to unlock Cookie Jar scenes, then return to the main menu to view them. The Summertime Saga app keeps these interactions simple enough that progress feels natural rather than overly grindy, though patience helps when chasing rare events.Mini-games and Activities VarietyMini-games add variety to everyday tasks, showing up in work shifts, school activities, and fitness challenges. Expect quick timing prompts, matching, or light reflex exercises that break up dialogue-heavy stretches. The difficulty is generally approachable, and you can retry if a task doesn’t click the first time.Because mini-games tie directly to characters and locations, they feel like part of the routine rather than separate modes. One moment you’re running a job, the next you’re training at the gym or helping with a class project. The Summertime Saga app uses these short bursts to pace longer routes while keeping the experience playful and engaging.Ongoing Updates, Community Support, and SavesSummertime Saga continues to grow through regular updates with a public roadmap, plus a strong community on Discord and a detailed wiki. Patreon support helps shape development, offering perks like private servers, bug tracking, and content polls that influence future releases. Stories expand over time, so returning after an update often reveals new arcs and scenes.Saves can be sensitive between versions, and the team recommends saving from the map or the main character’s bedroom for safer compatibility. Content is actively in development, so some routes remain incomplete until a later patch. The Summertime Saga app makes the most of its ongoing release cycle by keeping progress visible and giving players clear ways to find help if something breaks or changes.Summertime Saga Pros &amp; ConsRegular updates and community involvement shape both strengths and trade-offs for the Summertime Saga app. Most users will find a lot to explore, with some quirks typical of evolving games.ProsHuge cast and locations boost replay value.Free to download with a clear public roadmap.Active wiki and Discord provide helpful guidance.Varied mini-games keep pace lively.Optional Patreon perks deepen community involvement.ConsAdult content, not suitable for minors.Saves may not carry over between updates.Some stories remain incomplete during development.Download Summertime Saga APK on APKPureYou can download Summertime Saga APK latest version from APKPure. Depending on your network speed and device performance, the download may take a few minutes. APK size may vary by release, so ensure sufficient storage before starting, and expect standard Android install prompts.After installation, launch a New Game and explore the map to meet characters and trigger events. If updating, consider saving from the map or the main character’s bedroom beforehand for safer compatibility. For users who want the Summertime Saga latest version, check back regularly, as updates roll out on a consistent schedule. Enjoy at your own pace and remember the content is for mature audiences.","version":"21.0.0-wip.7164","operatingSystem":"ANDROID","applicationCategory":"GameApplication","applicationSubCategory":"Adventure","offers":{"@type":"Offer","price":"0.00","priceCurrency":"USD"},"datePublished":"2026-04-01","aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"8.0","ratingCount":562,"bestRating":10,"worstRating":1},"publisher":{"@type":"Thing","name":"DarkCookie"},"interactionStatistic":{"@type":"InteractionCounter","interactionType":"http://schema.org/DownloadAction","userInteractionCount":50000